---
import Layout from '~/layouts/Layout.astro';

const updated = '2026-04-29';
---

<Layout
  title="now"
  description="What Will Yennie is working on, learning, and looking for right now."
>
  <div class="container page prose">
    <header class="head">
      <h1>now</h1>
      <p class="meta">Updated {updated} ·
        <a href="https://nownownow.com/about" rel="noopener">/now page</a>
      </p>
    </header>

    <h2>Working on</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>This site, fast. Replacing the two-year-stale willyennie.com.</li>
      <li>A small library of "things I should have written down the first time."
        Internal notes I want to pull out into public posts.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Learning</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Reviewing system design for interviews.</li>
      <li>Soldering through a box of broken N64 cartridges.</li>
      <li>Reading <em>The End Is Always Near</em> by Dan Carlin.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Looking for</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>A full-stack role with real product surface. Language-agnostic;
        I care about the team and the problem more than the stack.</li>
      <li>Hard problems that reward going deep.</li>
      <li>Ideally NYC-friendly hours (remote or hybrid).</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Not doing</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Side-project sprawl. One thing at a time, finished.</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="footnote">
      This is a <a href="https://nownownow.com/about" rel="noopener">now page</a>,
      in the Sivers sense: what's actually true today, not a permanent bio.
    </p>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page { padding-block: var(--s-7) var(--s-8); }
  .head { margin-bottom: var(--s-6); }
  .head h1 { font-size: var(--fs-2xl); }
  .meta { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--fs-sm); color: var(--c-text-muted); margin-top: var(--s-2); }
  h2 {
    font-size: var(--fs-md);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--c-accent);
    margin-top: var(--s-6);
    margin-bottom: var(--s-3);
  }
  ul { padding-left: 1.25rem; }
  ul li { margin-bottom: var(--s-2); }
  .footnote {
    margin-top: var(--s-7);
    color: var(--c-text-muted);
    font-size: var(--fs-sm);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--c-border);
    padding-top: var(--s-4);
  }
</style>
